WEBVTT

00:22.840 --> 00:25.640
CHAPTER VII.

00:26.200 --> 00:30.100
Every man on this planet is taking his initiation in love.

00:31.020 --> 00:34.680
A new commandment I give unto you, that ye love one another.

00:35.820 --> 00:42.020
Ospensky states in Tertium Organum that love is a cosmic phenomenon,

00:43.200 --> 00:48.440
and opens to man the fourth-dimensional world, the world of the wondrous.

00:49.400 --> 00:52.860
Real love is selfish and free from fear.

00:53.580 --> 00:59.420
It pours itself out upon the object of its affection, without demanding any return.

01:00.280 --> 01:02.760
Its joy is in the joy of giving.

01:03.760 --> 01:09.580
Love is God in manifestation, and the strongest magnetic force in the universe.

01:10.720 --> 01:14.840
Pure unselfish love draws to itself its own.

01:14.840 --> 01:18.900
It does not need to seek or demand.

01:20.620 --> 01:24.320
Scarcely anyone has the faintest conception of real love.

01:25.240 --> 01:31.640
Man is selfish, tyrannical, or fearful in his affections, thereby losing the things he loves.

01:32.740 --> 01:37.680
Jealousy is the worst enemy of love, for the imagination runs riot,

01:37.680 --> 01:45.300
seeing the loved one attracted to another, and invariably these fears objectify if they are not

01:45.300 --> 01:53.360
neutralized. For example, a woman came to me in deep distress. The man she loved had left her for

01:53.360 --> 02:00.180
another woman, and said he never intended to marry her. She was torn with jealousy and resentment,

02:00.560 --> 02:05.380
and said she hoped he would suffer as he had made her suffer, and added,

02:05.380 --> 02:12.540
how could he leave me when I loved him so much? I replied, you are not loving that man,

02:12.740 --> 02:18.240
you are hating him, and added, you can never receive what you have never given.

02:18.820 --> 02:26.440
Give a perfect love, and you will receive a perfect love. Perfect yourself on this man.

02:26.960 --> 02:35.280
Give him a perfect unselfish love, demanding nothing in return. Do not criticize or condemn

02:35.280 --> 02:44.020
and bless him wherever he is. She replied, no, I won't bless him unless I know where he is.

02:44.980 --> 02:53.480
Well, I said, that is not real love. When you send out real love, real love will return to you,

02:53.800 --> 02:59.500
either from this man or his equivalent, for if this man is not the divine selection,

02:59.500 --> 03:06.460
you will not want him. As you are one with God, you are one with the love which belongs to you

03:06.460 --> 03:13.900
by divine right. Several months passed, and matters remained about the same, but she was

03:13.900 --> 03:20.900
working conscientiously within herself. I said, when you are no longer disturbed by his cruelty,

03:21.240 --> 03:26.680
he will cease to be cruel, as you are attracting it through your own emotions.

03:27.540 --> 03:32.420
Then I told her of a brotherhood in India who never said good morning to each other.

03:32.680 --> 03:40.340
They used these words, I salute the divinity in you. They saluted the divinity in every man,

03:40.680 --> 03:46.300
and in the wild animals in the jungle, and they were never harmed, for they saw only God in every

03:46.300 --> 03:54.900
living thing. I said, salute the divinity in this man, and say, I see your divine self only. I see

03:55.280 --> 04:05.360
as God sees you, perfect, made in his image and likeness. She found she was becoming more poised

04:05.360 --> 04:12.520
and gradually losing her resentment. He was a captain, and she always called him the cap.

04:13.860 --> 04:21.760
One day she said suddenly, God bless the cap wherever he is. I replied, now that is real love,

04:21.760 --> 04:28.280
and when you have become a complete circle, and are no longer disturbed by the situation,

04:28.740 --> 04:32.000
you will have his love, or attract its equivalent.

04:33.440 --> 04:38.800
I was moving at this time, and did not have a telephone, so was out of touch with her for

04:38.800 --> 04:45.680
a few weeks, when one morning I received a letter saying, we are married. At the earliest

04:45.680 --> 04:53.560
opportunity I paid her a call. My first words were, what happened? Oh, she exclaimed, a miracle.

04:54.140 --> 05:01.240
One day I woke up, and all suffering had ceased. I saw him that evening, and he asked me to marry

05:01.240 --> 05:06.980
him. We were married in about a week, and I have never seen a more devoted man.

05:09.180 --> 05:13.860
There is an old saying, no man is your enemy, no man is your friend,

05:14.420 --> 05:21.120
every man is your teacher. So one should become impersonal and learn what each man has to teach

05:21.120 --> 05:28.200
him, and soon he would learn his lessons and be free. The woman's lover was teaching her selfish

05:28.200 --> 05:35.580
love, which every man sooner or later must learn. Suffering is not necessary for man's development,

05:35.900 --> 05:42.060
it is the result of violation of spiritual law, but few people seem able to rouse themselves from

05:42.060 --> 05:48.740
their soul-sleep without it. When people are happy, they usually become selfish,

05:49.180 --> 05:55.900
and automatically the law of karma is set in action. Man often suffers loss through

05:55.900 --> 06:02.300
lack of appreciation. I knew a woman who had a very nice husband, but she said often,

06:02.680 --> 06:07.000
I don't care anything about being married, but that is nothing against my husband,

06:07.000 --> 06:14.100
I'm simply not interested in married life. She had other interests, and scarcely remembered she

06:14.100 --> 06:21.740
had a husband, she only thought of him when she saw him. One day her husband told her he was in

06:21.740 --> 06:28.540
love with another woman, and left. She came to me in distress and resentment. I replied,

06:29.220 --> 06:34.140
it is exactly what you spoke the word for, you said you didn't care anything about being married,

06:34.140 --> 06:41.680
so the subconscious worked to get you unmarried. She said, oh yes, I see, people get what they want,

06:41.880 --> 06:47.580
and then feel very much hurt. She soon became in perfect harmony with the situation,

06:47.980 --> 06:54.340
and knew they were both much happier apart. When a woman becomes indifferent or critical,

06:54.620 --> 07:00.680
and ceases to be an inspiration to her husband, he misses the stimulus of their early relationship,

07:00.680 --> 07:07.320
and is restless and unhappy. A man came to me dejected, miserable, and poor.

07:08.000 --> 07:14.120
His wife was interested in the science of numbers, and had had him read. It seems the

07:14.120 --> 07:19.860
report was not very favorable, for he said, my wife says I'll never amount to anything because

07:19.860 --> 07:26.920
I am a two. I replied, I don't care what your number is, you are a perfect idea in divine mind,

07:26.920 --> 07:33.400
and we will demand the success and prosperity which are already planned for you by that

07:33.400 --> 07:41.080
infinite intelligence. Within a few weeks he had a very fine position, and a year or two later

07:41.080 --> 07:48.240
he achieved a brilliant success as a writer. No man is a success in business unless he loves his

07:48.240 --> 07:56.300
work. The picture the artist paints for love of his art is his greatest work. The potboiler

07:56.300 --> 08:03.200
is always something to live down. No man can attract money if he despises it.

08:03.800 --> 08:09.580
Many people are kept in poverty by saying, money means nothing to me, I have a contempt

08:09.580 --> 08:16.400
for people who have it. This is the reason so many artists are poor. Their contempt for money

08:16.400 --> 08:22.640
separates them from it. I remember hearing one artist say of another, he's no good as an artist,

08:22.640 --> 08:28.860
but he has money in the bank. This attitude of mind, of course, separates man from his supply.

08:29.560 --> 08:35.600
He must be in harmony with a thing in order to attract it. Money is God in manifestation,

08:36.020 --> 08:43.820
as freedom from want and limitation, but it must be always kept in circulation and put to right

08:43.820 --> 08:52.180
uses. Hoarding and saving react with grim vengeance. This does not mean that man should not have houses

08:52.180 --> 09:00.400
and lots, stocks and bonds, for the barns of the righteous man shall be full. It means that man

09:00.400 --> 09:07.900
should not hoard even the principal if an occasion arises when money is necessary. In letting it go

09:07.900 --> 09:15.760
out fearlessly and cheerfully, he opens the way for more to come in, for God is man's unfailing

09:15.760 --> 09:23.180
and inexhaustible supply. This is the spiritual attitude towards money, and the great bank of

09:23.180 --> 09:30.720
the universal never fails. We see an example of hoarding in the film production of Greed.

09:31.640 --> 09:38.400
The woman won $5,000 in a lottery, but would not spend it. She hoarded and saved,

09:38.960 --> 09:44.560
let her husband suffer and starve, and eventually she scrubbed floors for a living.

09:45.280 --> 09:51.480
She loved the money itself and put it above everything, and one night she was murdered

09:51.480 --> 09:58.520
and the money taken from her. This is an example of where love of money is the root of all evil.

09:59.740 --> 10:06.660
Money in itself is good and beneficial, but used for destructive purposes, hoarded and saved,

10:07.080 --> 10:13.200
or considered more important than love, brings disease and disaster and the loss of the money

10:13.200 --> 10:22.140
itself. Follow the path of love, and all things are added, for God is love and God is supply.

10:23.160 --> 10:29.980
Follow the path of selfishness and greed, and the supply vanishes, or man is separated from it.

10:30.740 --> 10:37.820
For example, I knew the case of a very rich woman who hoarded her income. She rarely gave anything

10:37.820 --> 10:44.800
away, but bought and bought and bought things for herself. She was very fond of necklaces,

10:45.100 --> 10:49.240
and a friend once asked her how many she possessed. She replied,

10:49.620 --> 10:57.080
Sixty-seven. She bought them and put them away, carefully wrapped in tissue paper. Had she used

10:57.080 --> 11:04.180
the necklaces, it would have been quite legitimate, but she was violating the law of use. Her closets

11:04.180 --> 11:10.680
were filled with clothes she never wore, and jewels which never saw the light. The old woman's arms

11:10.680 --> 11:16.080
were gradually becoming paralyzed from holding on to things, and eventually she was considered

11:16.080 --> 11:21.900
incapable of looking after her affairs, and her wealth was handed over to others to manage.

11:23.020 --> 11:31.700
So man, in ignorance of the law, brings about his own destruction. All disease, all unhappiness,

11:31.700 --> 11:39.240
come from the violation of the law of love. Man's boomerangs of hate, resentment, and criticism

11:39.240 --> 11:47.000
come back laden with sickness and sorrow. Love seems almost a lost art, but the man with the

11:47.000 --> 11:54.500
knowledge of spiritual law knows it must be regained, for without it he has become as sounding

11:54.500 --> 12:02.840
brass and tinkling cymbals. For example, I had a student who came to me month after month to

12:02.840 --> 12:09.020
clean her consciousness of resentment. After a while she arrived at the point where she

12:09.020 --> 12:17.000
resented only one woman, but that one woman kept her busy. Little by little she became poised and

12:17.000 --> 12:24.720
harmonious, and one day all resentment was wiped out. She came in radiant and exclaimed,

12:25.200 --> 12:31.580
You can't understand how I feel. The woman said something to me, and instead of being furious,

12:32.040 --> 12:41.140
I was loving and kind. And she apologized and was perfectly lovely to me. No one can understand the

12:41.140 --> 12:48.780
lightness I feel within. Love and goodwill are invaluable in business. For example,

12:49.260 --> 12:55.320
a woman came to me complaining of her employer. She said she was cold and critical,

12:55.580 --> 13:03.400
and she knew she did not want her in the position. Well, I replied, salute the divinity in the woman

13:03.400 --> 13:12.460
and send her love. She said, I can't. She's a marble woman. I answered, You remember the story

13:12.460 --> 13:19.500
of the sculptor who asked for a certain piece of marble? He was asked why he wanted it, and he

13:19.500 --> 13:27.140
replied, because there is an angel in the marble. And out of it he produced a wonderful work of art.

13:27.920 --> 13:34.200
She said, Very well, I'll try it. A week later she came back and said,

13:34.440 --> 13:40.100
I did what you told me, and now the woman is very kind and took me out in her car.

13:44.260 --> 13:50.420
People are sometimes filled with remorse for having done someone an unkindness, perhaps years

13:50.420 --> 13:58.320
ago. If the wrong cannot be righted, its effect can be neutralized by doing someone a kindness

13:58.320 --> 14:06.700
in the present. This one thing I do, forgetting those things which are behind and reaching forth

14:06.700 --> 14:14.260
unto those things which are before. Sorrow, regret, and remorse tear down the cells of the body

14:14.260 --> 14:20.660
and poison the atmosphere of the individual. A woman said to me in deep sorrow,

14:21.260 --> 14:26.960
treat me to be happy and joyous, for my sorrow makes me so irritable with the members of my family

14:26.960 --> 14:33.420
that I keep making more karma. I was asked to treat a woman who was mourning for her daughter.

14:34.080 --> 14:39.260
I denied all belief in loss and separation and affirmed that God was the woman's joy,

14:39.260 --> 14:45.860
love, and peace. The woman gained her poise at once, but sent word by her son

14:45.860 --> 14:51.500
not to treat any longer, because she was so happy it wasn't respectable.

14:53.280 --> 15:01.780
So mortal mind loves to hang on to its griefs and regrets. I knew a woman who went about bragging

15:01.780 --> 15:08.140
of her troubles, so of course she always had something to brag about. The old idea was,

15:08.140 --> 15:15.300
if a woman did not worry about her children, she was not a good mother. Now we know that mother

15:15.300 --> 15:20.900
fear is responsible for many of the diseases and accidents which come into the lives of children,

15:21.400 --> 15:28.080
for fear pictures vividly the disease or situation feared, and these pictures objectify if not

15:28.080 --> 15:35.040
neutralized. Happy is the mother who can say sincerely that she puts her child in God's hands

15:35.040 --> 15:38.140
and therefore knows that he is divinely protected.

15:41.020 --> 15:47.000
For example, a woman awoke suddenly in the night, feeling her brother was in great danger.

15:47.500 --> 15:52.900
Instead of giving in to her fears, she commenced making statements of truth, saying,

15:53.440 --> 16:00.000
Man is a perfect idea in divine mind and is always in his right place. Therefore,

16:00.000 --> 16:07.380
my brother is in his right place and is divinely protected. The next day she found that her brother

16:07.380 --> 16:13.360
had been in close proximity to an explosion in a mine, but had miraculously escaped.

16:14.460 --> 16:20.940
So man is his brother's keeper in thought, and every man should know that the thing he loves

16:20.940 --> 16:27.560
dwells in the secret place of the Most High and abides under the shadow of the Almighty.

16:28.520 --> 16:35.040
There shall no evil befall thee, neither shall any plague come nigh thy dwelling.

16:36.000 --> 16:42.020
Perfect love casteth out fear, he that feareth is not made perfect in love,

16:42.420 --> 16:46.020
and love is the fulfilling of the law.

